<!DOCTYPE html>
<html style="margin: 0;padding: 0;">
<head>
    <title></title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 2px solid #FFF;">

<div style="background: #7a7a7a;padding: 1% 10%;border:2px solid #FFF;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">

    <p class="logo_name"
       style="font-size: 35px;font-weight: 600;color: #333; margin: 10px 0 10px 0;text-align: center;">
        <img src="https://www.ratingsville.com/assets/img/logo-8.png"
             style="width: 25%;position: relative;top: 10px;right: 10px;">
        <!-- Ratingsville -->
    </p>

    <div class="body" style="position:relative;min-height: 150px;background: #FFF;padding: 20px 40px;border-radius:6px">
        <h2 style="color: black;margin-bottom: 50px;font-weight:bold;">Hello <%= name %>,</h2>

        <p style="font-size: 17px;line-height: 24px;margin: 0 0 16px;">
            <% if (status === 'pending') { %>
                Your request for an appointment with <%= daycareName %> for <b><%= schedule %></b> has been successfully submitted. We will update you as soon as <%= daycareName %> responds to your request.
                To change your appointment date/time, please click <a href="https://www.ratingsville.com/#/daycare_appointment/<%= daycareId %>/<%= encodeURI(daycareName) %>?email=<%= encodeURI(email) %>&uid=<%= uid%>">reschedule</a>.
            <% } else if (status === 'approved') { %>
                Your appointment with <%= daycareName %> for <b><%= schedule %></b> has been confirmed. To change your appointment date/time, please click <a href="https://www.ratingsville.com/#/daycare_appointment/<%= daycareId %>/<%= encodeURI(daycareName) %>?email=<%= encodeURI(email) %>&uid=<%= uid%>">reschedule</a> to the Schedule Appointment tab of the child care whom user wants to reschedule with.
            <% } else { %>
                We understand you have chosen to cancel your appointment with <%= daycareName %> for <b><%= schedule %></b> and are processing your request. If you did not cancel your appointment, please
                <a href="https://www.ratingsville.com/#/contactus?type=appointment&id=<%= appointmentId %>&email=<%= encodeURI(email) %>&uid=<%= uid%>">contact us</a> and we will try our best (no guarantees though) to reschedule you for the same date and time.
            <% } %>
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 17px;line-height: 24px;margin: 0 0 16px;">
            Thank you for being a valued customer. We look forward to your continued partnership.
        </p>
        <br/>
        <p style="font-size: 17px;line-height: 24px;margin: 0 0 16px;">Sincerely,</p>
        <p style="font-size: 17px;line-height: 24px;margin: 0 0 16px;"><b>The Ratingsville Team </b></p>
        <hr style="border: none;border-bottom: 1px solid #ececec;margin: 40px 0 1.5rem 0;">
    </div>


    <div class="footer">
        <p style="padding-top: 20px; font-size: 14px;color: white;text-align: center;font-weight: 600;">Copyright &copy;
            2018 - Ratingsville</p>
    </div>
</div>
<div style="height: 5px;"></div>
</body>
</html>


